      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget-friendly ride to get you from point A to point B? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it's a well-used car that shows significant wear both inside and out. You'll notice cosmetic blemishes, interior wear, and it will likely need some mechanical attention. That said, it's a real opportunity for a handy buyer or someone who just needs basic transportation on a tight budget \u2014 and at this price, the value is hard to beat!",
