    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should come in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows noticeable wear including visible scratches, scuffs, and minor dents that reflect its age and use. Mechanically, it is functional and gets the job done for daily transportation, though some components may show signs of wear and could benefit from attention over time. The interior is used and shows its age, with worn upholstery and general signs of regular use. This is a solid budget option for someone who needs reliable transportation and is comfortable with a car that has some cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
