      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Fixer or Parts Car \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has seen better days and shows significant wear both inside and out. It may require mechanical attention and has noticeable body damage or cosmetic issues, so it's best suited for a handy buyer, a project enthusiast, or someone in need of an affordable short-term solution. What it lacks in polish, it makes up for in price \u2014 this is a no-frills, wallet-friendly opportunity for the right buyer! Come take a look and see if it fits your needs.",
