    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you an honest, complete picture before you buy. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light scuffs consistent with normal use. There are no major dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on the seats and trim that you'd expect from a regularly driven vehicle, but nothing that detracts significantly from usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts properly, and all major systems are functioning as expected. Brakes and tires have adequate life remaining, though a buyer should plan for routine maintenance in the normal course of ownership. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for someone looking for everyday reliability without paying a premium for near-mint condition.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
