    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered at $34,000, and that price honestly reflects its good overall condition \u2014 a solid, well-maintained used car that should serve its next owner reliably for years to come. The exterior presents well, with only minor wear consistent with normal use: a few small stone chips and light surface scratches here and there, but no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains good gloss and color uniformity. The interior is clean and functional \u2014 the seats show modest wear on the driver's side, the dashboard and trim are intact, and all major controls and features operate as expected. There are no torn panels or broken components. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and starts without hesitation. Routine maintenance has been kept reasonably up to date, and there are no warning lights on the dash. The tires have decent tread remaining, and the brakes feel responsive. This is not a perfect vehicle, but it is a genuinely good one \u2014 the kind of car you can drive home with confidence, without expecting any immediate major repairs. Ideal for a buyer looking for solid, everyday transportation at a fair price.",
